# Scroll-to-top fixed size

The scroll-to-top button must **not** change size at any breakpoint.

## Canonical dimensions

- Button: **62px** × **62px**
- Icon: **52px** × **52px**
- Padding: **5px** (use `px`, not `rem`/`em`)

## Rules

- Do **not** add responsive `width`, `height`, `padding`, or `--size` rules to `ScrollToTopButton.module.css`.
- Keep sizing decoupled from [`Icon.module.css`](src/components/Icon/Icon.module.css), which scales icons at `400px+`.
- If `Icon` breakpoints change, scroll-to-top must keep its own explicit `px` overrides on `.scroll-to-top__icon`.
- Do not switch padding to relative units — they can scale with global typography changes.
